      <PointerOffset>46800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>っと……料理、全部マスターしたみたい</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Uhm...It looks like we've mastered all recipes.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>46956</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さすが&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;だぁ～～。料理を全部覚えるなんて、
もう、『鬼に金棒』だ。いや、『仏に蓮華』だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>As expected of our dear, &lt;Mel&gt;! Being able to remember all these 
recipes is almost akin to a "demon's bat" or rather "Buddha's lotus."</EnglishText>
      <Notes>can be written better</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47020</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>意味わかんね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I don't get it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47088</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クゥリュ～～～？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Kyuruu...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47252</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>こんだけ美少女で、性格も良くて、気が利く&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;が
料理まで覚えたちゅーことは、もう無敵っちゅーことだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Not only is &lt;Mel&gt; beautiful, of good character, she can 
also master such a variety of recipes. She's nigh unrivalled!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47324</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>んだよ、無敵って……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Unrivalled...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47428</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もう、準備万端だで、いつでも嫁っこさ行けるだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>One could say that she's all ready to become
the perfect bride!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47520</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、そ、そんな、お嫁さんだなんて、私……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>A-A...bride...? No way...I'm humbled...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47644</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんな照れなくてもえーだーよ。
もーおらの方はいつでも準備ＯＫだで∀</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No need to be so embarrassed, dear!
I'm all prepared on my side~</EnglishText>
      <Notes>IS THIS MF FLIRTING WITHHER</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>47744</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_005_189_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>なんで、てめぇと結婚するって
話になってんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Why on earth did the conversation switched
to marriage!? Eugh!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
